      "difficulty": "Easy",
      "solution": "<p><img src=\"https://app-content.fly-assets.uk/fly/@width/image/jaoe38c1mobqiz0q/9987fb73-05de-4bea-ae39-8dba0745bfe2/f4cf82a0-3f36-11f1-8907-9d59f06ca3d8/file-jaoe38c1mobqiz0r.png?format=png\" data-orsrc=\"https://app-content.fly-assets.uk/image/jaoe38c1mobqiz0q/9987fb73-05de-4bea-ae39-8dba0745bfe2/f4cf82a0-3f36-11f1-8907-9d59f06ca3d8/file-jaoe38c1mobqiz0r.png\" loading=\"lazy\" style=\"max-width:100%;height:auto;display:block;margin:0 auto;max-height:40vh;vertical-align:baseline\" alt=\"JEE Main 2026 (Online) 6th April Morning Shift Chemistry - Coordination Compounds Question 3 English Explanation 1\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://app-content.fly-assets.uk/fly/@width/image/jaoe38c1mobqizss/f67a42e5-6f43-44cb-ae8f-f9fde9d53ff2/f5699fc0-3f36-11f1-8907-9d59f06ca3d8/file-jaoe38c1mobqizst.png?format=png\" data-orsrc=\"https://app-content.fly-assets.uk/image/jaoe38c1mobqizss/f67a42e5-6f43-44cb-ae8f-f9fde9d53ff2/f5699fc0-3f36-11f1-8907-9d59f06ca3d8/file-jaoe38c1mobqizst.png\" loading=\"lazy\" style=\"max-width:100%;height:auto;display:block;margin:0 auto;max-height:40vh;vertical-align:baseline\" alt=\"JEE Main 2026 (Online) 6th April Morning Shift Chemistry - Coordination Compounds Question 3 English Explanation 2\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://app-content.cdn.examgoal.net/fly/@width/image/6y3zli1mp044744/cc5814de-434c-49ce-9edd-020cb15bd2f5/e951ec40-4c9e-11f1-9864-53d65aa0ef81/file-6y3zli1mp044745.png?format=png\" data-orsrc=\"https://app-content.cdn.examgoal.net/image/6y3zli1mp044744/cc5814de-434c-49ce-9edd-020cb15bd2f5/e951ec40-4c9e-11f1-9864-53d65aa0ef81/file-6y3zli1mp044745.png\" loading=\"lazy\" style=\"max-width:100%;height:auto;display:block;margin:0 auto;max-height:40vh;vertical-align:baseline\" alt=\"JEE Main 2026 (Online) 6th April Morning Shift Chemistry - Coordination Compounds Question 3 English Explanation 3\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://app-content.fly-assets.uk/fly/@width/image/jaoe38c1mobqj13m/a0868c3f-6888-4867-ab50-1415891b8404/f66ae320-3f36-11f1-8907-9d59f06ca3d8/file-jaoe38c1mobqj13n.png?format=png\" data-orsrc=\"https://app-content.fly-assets.uk/image/jaoe38c1mobqj13m/a0868c3f-6888-4867-ab50-1415891b8404/f66ae320-3f36-11f1-8907-9d59f06ca3d8/file-jaoe38c1mobqj13n.png\" loading=\"lazy\" style=\"max-width:100%;height:auto;display:block;margin:0 auto;max-height:40vh;vertical-align:baseline\" alt=\"JEE Main 2026 (Online) 6th April Morning Shift Chemistry - Coordination Compounds Question 3 English Explanation 4\"></p>",
