      "subject": "Chemistry",
      "topic": "coordination-number",
      "difficulty": "Easy",
      "solution": "Here two O<sup>-</sup> + two N = 4 donar atoms present which can donate total 4 lone pair of electrons.\n<br><br>$$ \\therefore $$ It is tetradentate ligand.",
